sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant controller as WalletController
    participant auth as AuthGuard
    participant service as WalletService
    participant db as DataSource

    User->>controller: PUT /wallets/:id
    activate controller

    controller->>auth: validate JWT
    activate auth
    auth-->>controller: valid
    deactivate auth

    controller->>service: update(id, UpdateWalletDto)
    activate service

    service->>db: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    activate db

    db->>db: find wallet by id
    db->>db: verify wallet exists
    db->>db: update wallet with DTO data
    db->>db: COMMIT

    Note right of db: Update allowed fields:<br/>- bankId<br/>- bankAccountNumber

    db-->>service: success
    deactivate db

    service-->>controller: CustomApiResponse (200)
    deactivate service

    controller-->>User: HTTP 200 OK
    deactivate controller
